               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt,
                     Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 4ra-7vb)&#xD; I-2) Introductory
                     exhortation (fols. 7vb-8vc)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wäʾǝweddǝsaki ... “I
                     worship Thee ...” (fols. 8vc-9vc)&#xD; I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām: 179 miracles (fols.
                     10ra-156vc)&#xD; I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾsi ... "Does not the man ..." (distributed
                     among the miracles of Mary, fols. 66ra-90vc)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
